    </bf:content>
    <bf:tableOfContents>
      <bf:TableOfContents>
	<rdfs:label>v. 1. An introduction to covered bonds -- History of covered bonds outside the United States -- Covered bond case study : Germany -- Covered bond case study : United Kingdom -- Non-U.S. covered bonds market -- Covered bonds ratings -- Alternative funding sources -- History and development of covered bonds in the United States -- U.S. covered bond case study and regulatory framework -- Documentation of U.S. covered bonds -- v. 2. Appendices.</rdfs:label>
      </bf:TableOfContents>
    </bf:tableOfContents>
